name: DiaMetrics_lite
description: DiaMetrics (lite) is a web-based educational resource for exploring important concepts regarding binary classification (and its evaluation), which is important in many different fields such as psychodiagnostics (e.g. in determining cut-off values for tests), machine learning or medical testing.
